name: UInterchangeFbxTranslatorSettings
doc: Fbx translator class support import of texture, material, static mesh, skeletal mesh,

bConvertScene: Whether to convert FBX scene axis system to Unreal axis system.
bForceFrontXAxis: Whether to force the front axis to be align with X instead of -Y default.
bConvertSceneUnit: Whether to convert the scene from FBX unit to UE unit (centimeter).
